<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Opening Minute AI</h3>

<ol class="govuk-list govuk-list--number govuk-list--spaced">
  <li>
    <strong>Open the MinuteUrl</strong>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Click the <strong>MinuteUrl</strong> link from CloudFormation Outputs, or paste it into a new browser tab.
    </p>
  </li>

  <li>
    <strong>Enter your credentials</strong>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      When prompted with the browser's authentication dialog, enter the <strong>BasicAuthUsername</strong>
      and <strong>BasicAuthPassword</strong> from the CloudFormation Outputs tab.
    </p>
  </li>

  <li>
    <strong>View the homepage</strong>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      After logging in, you will see the Minute AI homepage.
    </p>
  </li>
</ol>

<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">What you should see</h3>

<p class="govuk-body">
  After logging in, you should see:
</p>

<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
  <li>The Minute AI homepage with a clean, modern interface</li>
  <li>A prominent <strong>"New meeting"</strong> button</li>
  <li>A list of any existing meetings (empty on first use)</li>
  <li>Navigation options including Templates</li>
</ul>

